Blue
====

Blue is a content management system foundation used to create adminable websites.


Install
=======

0. Prerequisites:

script/plugin install git://github.com/collectiveidea/awesome_nested_set.git
script/plugin install git://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip.git
script/plugin install git://github.com/jackdempsey/acts_as_commentable.git
script/plugin install git://github.com/rsl/stringex.git
script/plugin install git://github.com/mislav/will_paginate.git

1. Add as a submodule
git submodule add git@github.com:bluespan/blue.git vendor/plugins/blue
git submodule init
git submodule update

2. Bootstrap
rake blue:bootstrap

3. Install gems
rake gems:install

4. Run Migrations
rake db:migrate

5. Create Admin
rake blue:create:admin

6. Remove default routes
map.connect ':controller/:action/:id'
map.connect ':controller/:action/:id.:format'

7. Launch server
script/server

